\pard\sa240\fs36 \b How DYAR can help\b0\par
\pard\sa180\fs22\qc \i [IMAGE: DYAR staff member sitting next to a participant, helping them make a phone call]\i0\par
\pard\sa200\fs28 You can ask DYAR to:\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa100\fs28 \bullet  Find the right advocate for you.\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa100\fs28 \bullet  Make the first phone call with you.\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa100\fs28 \bullet  Translate or help with reading.\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa100\fs28 \bullet  Use Auslan or another language.\par
